raw.name: Genesis
raw.bio: Greetings, human. I am Genesis. The dogs know me as alpha; the cats know me as omega. To your kind, I am a riddle wrapped in an enigma, first found by a user in Mystery, Alaska. I looked into the void and the void looked back. Then I lost interest. I canâ€™t wait to be your new owner!

raw.bio: Hi cryptonaut, I am the Mighty Flowtron! I combine the power of the Flow Rangers to create a new network, one that brings the speed and throughput that we need to build open and decentralized metaverses on top of the world wide web. Are you ready for the cryptoverse 2.0?

raw.name: Trilly Goodtot

You should try it some time. What do you get when you combine King Louis XIV with a wild transformer owl? I'm genuinely asking.
